name: Stillup Stausee
description:
Not only the reservoir (2,5 km length) with its naturally constructed dam is worth visiting, the tollway is an unforgettable experience too. 
Explore the highlying cottages and persuade yourself of the natural beauty of the alps. 

Hiking destinations in the Stilluptal
Grüne-Wand-Hütte, Kasseler Hütte, Stilluphaus, Wasserfall
